name: W0-W1-33 | WowieJam 4.0 Submission
description:

This game was created by @TjarkiBoi and @mapleink.games (aka. thunderboii_) during the WOWIEEE!! Jam 4.0 ! We put a lot of work, sleepless nights and rage quits into this, so u can enjoy playing it. We hope you will enjoy the game and that you'll have fun!
